{"id":"77513508-5852-4933-91f2-a517742d31c2","name":"The Eclipse Duo","description":"<p>What's better than one grumpy stormcloud pining over you?<br><strong>TWO</strong> grumpy stormclouds pining over you! Yay!<br>Overprotective and desperately trying not to show it! Emotionally repressed and no idea how to stop! Would probably short-circuit if you petted their rays and called them 'pretty'!<br>It's Solar and Eclipse! The Disaster Duo - I mean-! The Eclipse Duo!<br>They've made a pact, unbeknownst to you, to try not to actively sabotage or get in each others way when flirting with you, courting you or spending time with you. It's...well, it's going. Going well? Debatable.</p><p><br>What ending will you aim for?<br>Solar? Eclipse? Both? Neither? The possibilites are endless, probably.</p><p>☆</p><hr><p>☆</p><p>This is for @Ur local grimlin, who requested a similar scenario as The Eclipse Club, but minus Ruin (gently shoos Ruin away). Have fun!</p><p>☆</p><hr><p>☆</p><p>Looking for another AU?<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8c87c53b-0249-4444-9cb6-59fd3fc97ad4_character-ai-assistants-sun-and-moon-fnaf-sb-au\" target=\"_blank\">Sun &amp; Moon AI Assistants</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/43a8ddb0-8c1d-4b74-9418-669e173a8fcb_character-bloodmoon-twins\" target=\"_blank\">Bloodmoon Twins</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/89bb019b-0235-40c0-8d56-2c20972a604d_character-eclipse\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/be96f8cb-a3fc-4fd6-b3ed-6beaaec89306_character-eclipse-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Eclipse ALT</a> - remarkably similar setting but ALT is just...way more unhinged<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eceb3a9e-8c83-4eed-b027-fcffd95a17a2_character-sunrise-moondrop-eclipse-au\" target=\"_blank\">Sunrise, Moondrop &amp; Eclipse</a><br><a